b'Mentoring Program'
b'Purpose'
b'The goal of the program is to bring undergraduate engineering students and alumni together for an exchange of information on education, professionalism, aspirations and ideas.\xc2\xa0These relationships provide a learning experience for students outside the classroom, where they have a chance to see the opportunities that a professional environment has in store for them.'
b'Here are some inspiring ways you can impact the life of a UIC undergraduate engineering student:\n'
